\par\pard\plain \li720\ri-720\qc\ltrch\loch {\f1\fs24\b0\i0\ul\ulc0\cf1 ACT 2}
\par\pard\plain \li720\ri-720\sb480\sl-240\slmult0\ql\ltrch\loch {\f2\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 INT. SMALL HOSPITAL TYPE ROOM}
\par\pard\plain \li720\ri-720\sb240\sl-240\slmult0\ql\ltrch\loch {\f2\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 Aaron is strapped to a wheelchair. He's dressed in a day-glow orange shirt with matching pants. His head is shaved. A stern looking woman in uniform is standing to one side with a clipboard. A man in a brown jump suit stands behind the chair, one hand on Aaron's shoulder. }
\par\pard\plain \li3600\ri-360\sb240\sl-240\slmult0\ql\ltrch\loch {\f2\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 LAWYER}
\par\pard\plain \li2160\ri1440\sl-240\slmult0\ql\ltrch\loch {\f2\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 Can't we give him a moment? The download just finished decompressing, he won't even know where he is!}
\par\pard\plain \li3600\ri-360\sb240\sl-240\slmult0\ql\ltrch\loch {\f2\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 OFFICER}
\par\pard\plain \li2160\ri1440\sl-240\slmult0\ql\ltrch\loch {\f2\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 The subject is allowed 5 minutes to prepare for their hearing.}
\par\pard\plain \li720\ri-720\sb240\sl-240\slmult0\ql\ltrch\loch {\f2\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 Aaron seems to be waking from a head injury. His eyes open slowly he draws a deep breath. His lawyer slaps him on the shoulders from behind the chair and leans in.}
\par\pard\plain \li3600\ri-360\sb240\sl-240\slmult0\ql\ltrch\loch {\f2\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 LAWYER}
\par\pard\plain \li2160\ri1440\sl-240\slmult0\ql\ltrch\loch {\f2\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 Aaron? I need you awake, are you awake Aaron?}
\par\pard\plain \li3600\ri-360\sb240\sl-240\slmult0\ql\ltrch\loch {\f2\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 AARON}
\par\pard\plain \li2160\ri1440\sl-240\slmult0\ql\ltrch\loch {\f2\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 Um, yeah. Wait, where am I? What's going on? Where's Ivy?}
\par\pard\plain \li3600\ri-360\sb240\sl-240\slmult0\ql\ltrch\loch {\f2\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 LAWYER}
\par\pard\plain \li2160\ri1440\sl-240\slmult0\ql\ltrch\loch {\f2\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 You're about to be put on trial for a very serious crime. I need you to understand what's going on so you can handle the questioning.}
\par\pard\plain \li3600\ri-360\sb240\sl-240\slmult0\ql\ltrch\loch {\f2\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 AARON}
\par\pard\plain \li2160\ri1440\sl-240\slmult0\ql\ltrch\loch {\f2\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 What trial? What happened?}
\par\pard\plain \li3600\ri-360\sb240\sl-240\slmult0\ql\ltrch\loch {\f2\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 LAWYER}
\par\pard\plain \li2160\ri1440\sl-240\slmult0\ql\ltrch\loch {\f2\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 Your actions have lead to a fractal disruption in our time-line. This is a very serious crime. Do you understand me?}
\par\pard\plain \li3600\ri-360\sb240\sl-240\slmult0\ql\ltrch\loch {\f2\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 AARON}
\par\pard\plain \li2160\ri1440\sl-240\slmult0\ql\ltrch\loch {\f2\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 No. I have no idea what you're talking about. All I need to know right now, is what happened to us?}
\par\pard\plain \li720\ri-720\sb240\sl-240\slmult0\ql\ltrch\loch {\f2\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 The lawyer shrugs and looks up to the officer for assistance. The officer flips over a few pages on their clipboard.}
\par\pard\plain \li3600\ri-360\sb240\sl-240\slmult0\ql\ltrch\loch {\f2\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 OFFICER}
\par\pard\plain \li2160\ri1440\sl-240\slmult0\ql\ltrch\loch {\f2\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 The subject arrived with a woman. Her current whereabouts are not listed here.}
\par\pard\plain \li3600\ri-360\sb240\sl-240\slmult0\ql\ltrch\loch {\f2\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 LAWYER}
\par\pard\plain \li2160\ri1440\sl-240\slmult0\ql\ltrch\loch {\f2\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 She's not been implicated in the crime, I'm sure she's fine. You, on the other hand, are in a great deal of trouble.}
\par\pard\plain \li3600\ri-360\sb240\sl-240\slmult0\ql\ltrch\loch {\f2\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 AARON}
\par\pard\plain \li2160\ri1440\sl-240\slmult0\ql\ltrch\loch {\f2\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 For what? I just got here, you've got me confused with somebody else!}
\par\pard\plain \li3600\ri-360\sb240\sl-240\slmult0\ql\ltrch\loch {\f2\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 LAWYER}
\par\pard\plain \li2160\ri1440\sl-240\slmult0\ql\ltrch\loch {\f2\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 I'm sure from your perspective it seems like you just got here, but you were activated days ago. Since then you managed to avoid setting a restore point before you ultimately escaped through the World Gate. From there you allegedly broke many of our laws governing technology and time travel.}
\par\pard\plain \li3600\ri-360\sb240\sl-240\slmult0\ql\ltrch\loch {\f2\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 AARON}
\par\pard\plain \li2160\ri1440\sl-240\slmult0\ql\ltrch\loch {\f2\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 Time travel? Are you kidding me?}
\par\pard\plain \li3600\ri-360\sb240\sl-240\slmult0\ql\ltrch\loch {\f2\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 LAWYER}
\par\pard\plain \li2160\ri1440\sl-240\slmult0\ql\ltrch\loch {\f2\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 Yes, I know it can be a lot to accept right now but I only have a few minutes to catch you up to speed. }
\par\pard\plain \li3600\ri-360\sb240\sl-240\slmult0\ql\ltrch\loch {\f2\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 AARON}
\par\pard\plain \li2160\ri1440\sl-240\slmult0\ql\ltrch\loch {\f2\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 Why don't I remember any of this? Where am I? How could I possibly have broken any laws?}
\par\pard\plain \li720\ri-720\sb240\sl-240\slmult0\ql\ltrch\loch {\f2\fs24 The Lawyer draws back the curtain at the end of the room revealing a view of the upper floors if a few of large buildings across the street. Between them a sparkling body of water stretches to a distant shore, covered in familiar featureless gray buildings.}
\par\pard\plain \li3600\ri-360\sb240\sl-240\slmult0\ql\ltrch\loch {\f2\fs24 AARON}
\par\pard\plain \li2160\ri1440\sl-240\slmult0\ql\ltrch\loch {\f2\fs24 Is that Chicago? Am I inside the dome?}
\par\pard\plain \li3600\ri-360\sb240\sl-240\slmult0\ql\ltrch\loch {\f2\fs24 LAWYER}
\par\pard\plain \li2160\ri1440\sl-240\slmult0\ql\ltrch\loch {\f2\fs24 Yes, you arrived a few days ago with a woman.}
\par\pard\plain \li3600\ri-360\sb240\sl-240\slmult0\ql\ltrch\loch {\f2\fs24 AARON}
\par\pard\plain \li2160\ri1440\sl-240\slmult0\ql\ltrch\loch {\f2\fs24 YES! Ivy! Why is she not here?}
\par\pard\plain \li3600\ri-360\sb240\sl-240\slmult0\ql\ltrch\loch {\f2\fs24 LAWYER}
\par\pard\plain \li2160\ri1440\sl-240\slmult0\ql\ltrch\loch {\f2\fs24 She's not the one in trouble, Aaron. She'll be notified once you're sentenced. }
\par\pard\plain \li3600\ri-360\sb240\sl-240\slmult0\ql\ltrch\loch {\f2\fs24 AARON}
\par\pard\plain \li2160\ri1440\sl-240\slmult0\ql\ltrch\loch {\f2\fs24 Sentenced! I didn't even do anything!}
\par\pard\plain \li3600\ri-360\sb240\sl-240\slmult0\ql\ltrch\loch {\f2\fs24 LAWYER}
\par\pard\plain \li2160\ri1440\sl-240\slmult0\ql\ltrch\loch {\f2\fs24 I'm sure you don't remember, but we have indisputable evidence of your crimes.}
\par\pard\plain \li3600\ri-360\sb240\sl-240\slmult0\ql\ltrch\loch {\f2\fs24 AARON}
\par\pard\plain \li2160\ri1440\sl-240\slmult0\ql\ltrch\loch {\f2\fs24 That's impossible! You're accusing me of doing things I have no memory of!}
\par\pard\plain \li3600\ri-360\sb240\sl-240\slmult0\ql\ltrch\loch {\f2\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 LAWYER}
\par\pard\plain \li2160\ri1440\sl-240\slmult0\ql\ltrch\loch {\f2\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 The crime you're accused of is extremely serious. And your memory is the best we could do given the circumstances.}
\par\pard\plain \li3600\ri-360\sb240\sl-240\slmult0\ql\ltrch\loch {\f2\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 AARON}
\par\pard\plain \li2160\ri1440\sl-240\slmult0\ql\ltrch\loch {\f2\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 What do you mean?}
\par\pard\plain \li3600\ri-360\sb240\sl-240\slmult0\ql\ltrch\loch {\f2\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 LAWYER}
\par\pard\plain \li2160\ri1440\sl-240\slmult0\ql\ltrch\loch {\f2\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 The body we've activated for you is a copy of the body you arrived in. The original organic material doesn't survive the transfer. We construct an identical copy, matched at the atomic level, out of programmable particles. Your mind shouldn't be able to tell the difference. }
\par\pard\plain \li720\ri-720\sb240\sl-240\slmult0\ql\ltrch\loch {\f2\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 Aaron is silent for a moment while he tries to get a read from the faces of his captors. They seem deadly serious.}
\par\pard\plain \li3600\ri-360\sb240\sl-240\slmult0\ql\ltrch\loch {\f2\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 AARON}
\par\pard\plain \li2160\ri1440\sl-240\slmult0\ql\ltrch\loch {\f2\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 This is insane! Let me out of this chair!}
\par\pard\plain \li720\ri-720\sb240\sl-240\slmult0\ql\ltrch\loch {\f2\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 Aaron struggles against the straps to no avail.}
\par\pard\plain \li3600\ri-360\sb240\sl-240\slmult0\ql\ltrch\loch {\f2\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 LAWYER}
\par\pard\plain \li2160\ri1440\sl-240\slmult0\ql\ltrch\loch {\f2\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 Under normal circumstances, people save restore points we call "images" on the city mainframe in case of catastrophic damage. If the body is somehow destroyed we can construct a new copy from the last image. Since you never made another restore point - the only one on file was from your original transfer to the city. So we built you from that image. }
\par\pard\plain \li3600\ri-360\sb240\sl-240\slmult0\ql\ltrch\loch {\f2\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 AARON}
\par\pard\plain \li2160\ri1440\sl-240\slmult0\ql\ltrch\loch {\f2\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 So you're saying this isn't even the first body you've copied for me?}
\par\pard\plain \li3600\ri-360\sb240\sl-240\slmult0\ql\ltrch\loch {\f2\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 LAWYER}
\par\pard\plain \li2160\ri1440\sl-240\slmult0\ql\ltrch\loch {\f2\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 Since the actions you're accused of have caused a fractal disruption in the time-line, it's impossible to say how many copies there are.}
\par\pard\plain \li3600\ri-360\sb240\sl-240\slmult0\ql\ltrch\loch {\f2\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 AARON}
\par\pard\plain \li2160\ri1440\sl-240\slmult0\ql\ltrch\loch {\f2\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 What are you saying? What happened to me?}
\par\pard\plain \li3600\ri-360\sb240\sl-240\slmult0\ql\ltrch\loch {\f2\fs24 LAWYER}
\par\pard\plain \li2160\ri1440\sl-240\slmult0\ql\ltrch\loch {\f2\fs24 This city, in this moment is special. It was anchored here and now at the great expense and sacrifice of people who won't be born for generations.}
\par\pard\plain \li3600\ri-360\sb240\sl-240\slmult0\ql\ltrch\loch {\f2\fs24 AARON}
\par\pard\plain \li2160\ri1440\sl-240\slmult0\ql\ltrch\loch {\f2\fs24 I'm in the future?}
\par\pard\plain \li3600\ri-360\sb240\sl-240\slmult0\ql\ltrch\loch {\f2\fs24 LAWYER}
\par\pard\plain \li2160\ri1440\sl-240\slmult0\ql\ltrch\loch {\f2\fs24 No, you're in the past. At least, from the perspective of everyone who lives here.}
\par\pard\plain \li3600\ri-360\sb240\sl-240\slmult0\ql\ltrch\loch {\f2\fs24 AARON}
\par\pard\plain \li2160\ri1440\sl-240\slmult0\ql\ltrch\loch {\f2\fs24 So you're time travelers?}
\par\pard\plain \li3600\ri-360\sb240\sl-240\slmult0\ql\ltrch\loch {\f2\fs24 LAWYER}
\par\pard\plain \li2160\ri1440\sl-240\slmult0\ql\ltrch\loch {\f2\fs24 We have a connection from this anchor to another. A two way bridge through which we can trade resources and personnel.}
\par\pard\plain \li3600\ri-360\sb240\sl-240\slmult0\ql\ltrch\loch {\f2\fs24 AARON}
\par\pard\plain \li2160\ri1440\sl-240\slmult0\ql\ltrch\loch {\f2\fs24 What does that have to do with me?}
\par\pard\plain \li3600\ri-360\sb240\sl-240\slmult0\ql\ltrch\loch {\f2\fs24 LAWYER}
\par\pard\plain \li2160\ri1440\sl-240\slmult0\ql\ltrch\loch {\f2\fs24 Your misuse of the gateway between worlds has broken the stability we count on to maintain that connection.}
\par\pard\plain \li3600\ri-360\sb240\sl-240\slmult0\ql\ltrch\loch {\f2\fs24 AARON}
\par\pard\plain \li2160\ri1440\sl-240\slmult0\ql\ltrch\loch {\f2\fs24 But I've never even seen this gateway!}
\par\pard\plain \li3600\ri-360\sb240\sl-240\slmult0\ql\ltrch\loch {\f2\fs24 LAWYER}
\par\pard\plain \li2160\ri1440\sl-240\slmult0\ql\ltrch\loch {\f2\fs24 You have, and you will.}
\par\pard\plain \li720\ri-720\sb240\sl-240\slmult0\ql\ltrch\loch {\f2\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 A massive blast rocks the building. The explosion shakes the room and the lights flicker. A loud fire alarm rings out and yellow flashing lights illuminate the room through the windows facing the hallway. Two robotic humanoid guards enter the room with what appear to be large automatic weapons in their black metallic hands. Despite their obvious mechanical construction, they move and sound remarkably like humans.}
\par\pard\plain \li3600\ri-360\sb240\sl-240\slmult0\ql\ltrch\loch {\f2\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 GUARD 1}
\par\pard\plain \li2160\ri1440\sl-240\slmult0\ql\ltrch\loch {\f2\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 This building is being evacuated. We will escort you to safety.}
\par\pard\plain \li3600\ri-360\sb240\sl-240\slmult0\ql\ltrch\loch {\f2\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 OFFICER}
\par\pard\plain \li2160\ri1440\sl-240\slmult0\ql\ltrch\loch {\f2\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 This subject is awaiting immediate trial and cannot be moved off-site.}
\par\pard\plain \li3600\ri-360\sb240\sl-240\slmult0\ql\ltrch\loch {\f2\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 LAWYER}
\par\pard\plain \li2160\ri1440\sl-240\slmult0\ql\ltrch\loch {\f2\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 I'll take responsibility for him, he doesn't even know where he is.}
\par\pard\plain \li3600\ri-360\sb240\sl-240\slmult0\ql\ltrch\loch {\f2\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 OFFICER}
\par\pard\plain \li2160\ri1440\sl-240\slmult0\ql\ltrch\loch {\f2\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 That is unacceptable. (to one of the guards) Terminate the subject, we'll rebuild him for when the trial is rescheduled.}
\par\pard\plain \li3600\ri-360\sb240\sl-240\slmult0\ql\ltrch\loch {\f2\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 LAWYER}
\par\pard\plain \li2880\ri2160\sl-240\slmult0\ql\ltrch\loch {\f2\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 (to Aaron)}
\par\pard\plain \li2160\ri1440\sl-240\slmult0\ql\ltrch\loch {\f2\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 Ugh, sorry buddy. I tried.}
\par\pard\plain \li720\ri-720\sb240\sl-240\slmult0\ql\ltrch\loch {\f2\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 Guard 1 leads the Officer and the Lawyer out of the room. Guard 2 arms his rifle and watches them leave.}
\par\pard\plain \li3600\ri-360\sb240\sl-240\slmult0\ql\ltrch\loch {\f2\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 AARON}
\par\pard\plain \li2880\ri2160\sl-240\slmult0\ql\ltrch\loch {\f2\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 (yelling after them)}
\par\pard\plain \li2160\ri1440\sl-240\slmult0\ql\ltrch\loch {\f2\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 You can't do this! I didn't do anything!}
\par\pard\plain \li3600\ri-360\sb240\sl-240\slmult0\ql\ltrch\loch {\f2\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 GUARD 2}
\par\pard\plain \li2160\ri1440\sl-240\slmult0\ql\ltrch\loch {\f2\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 Ah, but you did.}
\par\pard\plain \li720\ri-720\sb240\sl-240\slmult0\ql\ltrch\loch {\f2\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 Guard 2 checks for others in either direction of the hallway and then walks over to Aaron's chair.}
\par\pard\plain \li3600\ri-360\sb240\sl-240\slmult0\ql\ltrch\loch {\f2\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 AARON}
\par\pard\plain \li2160\ri1440\sl-240\slmult0\ql\ltrch\loch {\f2\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 Please no, this is a terrible mistake!}
\par\pard\plain \li3600\ri-360\sb240\sl-240\slmult0\ql\ltrch\loch {\f2\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 GUARD 2}
\par\pard\plain \li2160\ri1440\sl-240\slmult0\ql\ltrch\loch {\f2\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 You may not know it, but you are uniquely qualified to save millions of people. }
\par\pard\plain \li720\ri-720\sb240\sl-240\slmult0\ql\ltrch\loch {\f2\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 Guard 2 holsters his rifle and bends over to release Aaron's legs at the base of the chair.}
\par\pard\plain \li3600\ri-360\sb240\sl-240\slmult0\ql\ltrch\loch {\f2\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 AARON}
\par\pard\plain \li2160\ri1440\sl-240\slmult0\ql\ltrch\loch {\f2\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 What are you talking about? You're not going to kill me?}
\par\pard\plain \li3600\ri-360\sb240\sl-240\slmult0\ql\ltrch\loch {\f2\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 GUARD 2}
\par\pard\plain \li2160\ri1440\sl-240\slmult0\ql\ltrch\loch {\f2\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 Nothing can kill you Aaron, your body is already dead. Will you trust me while I attempt to aid your escape?}
\par\pard\plain \li720\ri-720\sb240\sl-240\slmult0\ql\ltrch\loch {\f2\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 Guard 2 pauses at Aaron's wrist restraints and waits for an answer. Aaron anxiously watches for his hands to be freed.}
\par\pard\plain \li3600\ri-360\sb240\sl-240\slmult0\ql\ltrch\loch {\f2\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 AARON}
\par\pard\plain \li2160\ri1440\sl-240\slmult0\ql\ltrch\loch {\f2\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 Yes, absolutely!}
\par\pard\plain \li720\ri-720\sb240\sl-240\slmult0\ql\ltrch\loch {\f2\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 The moment Guard 2 removes the wrist restraints Aaron snaps to his feet. He pushes past Guard 2 and runs to the door. Without hesitation he chooses to run left out of the doorway and down the hall. }
\par\pard\plain \li720\ri-720\sb480\sl-240\slmult0\ql\ltrch\loch {\f2\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 INT. STERILE WHITE HALLWAY}
\par\pard\plain \li720\ri-720\sb240\sl-240\slmult0\ql\ltrch\loch {\f2\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 Aaron slows down to turn a corner when the wheel chair catches up to him from behind and he slams back into the seat. The chair continues forward, much faster than he was running. Guard 2 is pushing it while running at an astonishing pace.}
\par\pard\plain \li3600\ri-360\sb240\sl-240\slmult0\ql\ltrch\loch {\f2\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 GUARD 2}
\par\pard\plain \li2160\ri1440\sl-240\slmult0\ql\ltrch\loch {\f2\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 Please remain seated, Aaron. I'll do what I can to ensure your safety.}
\par\pard\plain \li720\ri-720\sb240\sl-240\slmult0\ql\ltrch\loch {\f2\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 Aaron mutters a few curse words while the chair rockets down the hall. They pass a few people in uniform who are unable to do more than yell at them as they pass. The Guard continues to push Aaron to an intersection, rounds the corner and continues down the next hall to an elevator. The robot grabs the wheels suddenly and locks them up, screeching to a halt precisely at the elevator doors.}
\par\pard\plain \li3600\ri-360\sb240\sl-240\slmult0\ql\ltrch\loch {\f2\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 GUARD 2}
\par\pard\plain \li2160\ri1440\sl-240\slmult0\ql\ltrch\loch {\f2\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 Would you mind pushing the call button, Aaron?}
\par\pard\plain \li720\ri-720\sb240\sl-240\slmult0\ql\ltrch\loch {\f2\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 Aaron only turns to look at the Guard in shock. Guard 2 reaches over Aaron with the end of his rifle and calmly pushes the down arrow. There is only a brief moment of silence before the doors open. The Guard pushes Aaron inside, next to a man and woman both wearing similar brown jump-suits as Aaron's Lawyer. Aaron tries not to look at either one of them. The doors close, the car begins to descend.}
\par\pard\plain \li720\ri-720\sb480\sl-240\slmult0\ql\ltrch\loch {\f2\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 INT.INSIDE THE ELEVATOR}
\par\pard\plain \li3600\ri-360\sb240\sl-240\slmult0\ql\ltrch\loch {\f2\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 MAN IN ELEVATOR}
